    {
      "id": 17,
      "title": "Alert Rules Reference",
      "description": "Summary of all alert rules for the Documentation Generator agent with conditions, severity, and notification channels.",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 59 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## EUDR-030 Documentation Generator Alert Rules\n\n| # | Alert | Condition | Severity | Evaluation | Action |\n|---|-------|-----------|----------|------------|--------|\n| 1 | **Rejected Submissions** | gl_eudr_dgn_rejected_submissions > 0 for 1h | Warning | Every 5m, for 15m | Review rejection reasons, amend DDS documents |\n| 2 | **Critical Rejections** | gl_eudr_dgn_rejected_submissions > 10 for 30m | Critical | Every 5m, for 5m | Page on-call, activate emergency amendment workflow |\n| 3 | **Pending Submission Backlog** | gl_eudr_dgn_pending_submissions > 20 for 4h | Warning | Every 15m, for 1h | Check EU IS connectivity, review submission queue |\n| 4 | **Validation Failure Rate** | validation invalid rate > 30% for 1h | Warning | Every 5m, for 30m | Review document templates, check data quality upstream |\n| 5 | **High API Error Rate** | API 5xx error rate > 1% for 5 minutes | Critical | Every 1m, for 5m | Page on-call, check infrastructure |\n| 6 | **DDS Generation Latency** | p99 > 5s for 10 minutes | Warning | Every 5m, for 10m | Investigate performance, check database queries |\n\n### Notification Channels\n- **Critical**: PagerDuty + Slack #eudr-critical + Email compliance-lead\n- **Warning**: Slack #eudr-alerts + Email on-call\n\n### Runbook Links\n- [Rejected Submissions Response](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/dgn/rejected-submissions)\n- [Submission Backlog Resolution](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/dgn/submission-backlog)\n- [Validation Failure Investigation](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/dgn/validation-failures)\n- [DDS Generation Troubleshooting](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/dgn/dds-generation)\n- [EU IS Connectivity Issues](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/dgn/eu-is-connectivity)\n- [Performance Degradation](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/dgn/perf-degradation)"
      }
    }
